<div class="services">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="mid_agile_bannner_top_info">
            <h1 class="tittle_agile_w3">Portfolio</h1>
            <div class="heading-underline">
                <div class="h-u1"></div><div class="h-u2"></div><div class="h-u3"></div><div class="clearfix"></div>
            </div>
            <p>At Media Gate Studios  ,We team up to create high quality for a diverse number of companies ,products ,services and marketing needs. Our work is available on various media platform ,you can view below: </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mid_agile_bannner_top_info">
            <h4 class="tittle_agile_w3">Commercials</h4>
            <div class="heading-underline">
                <div class="h-u1"></div><div class="h-u2"></div><div class="h-u3"></div><div class="clearfix"></div>
            </div>
            <p>We manage every aspect of a commercial’s physical production from creative development, casting, and scriptwriting, to shooting, editing, visual effects, graphics, voice-over, music, finishing, and broadcast delivery. With a set of high quality equipements and universal minds.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mid_agile_bannner_top_info">
            <h4 class="tittle_agile_w3">Broadcast production</h4>
            <div class="heading-underline">
                <div class="h-u1"></div><div class="h-u2"></div><div class="h-u3"></div><div class="clearfix"></div>
            </div>
            <p>Our experience and expertise, as well as our relationships with production experts, allow us to create creative broadcast content tailor-made to each of our client's needs. We guarantee high quality, creative and out of the box approaches that fit for your needs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mid_agile_bannner_top_info">
            <h4 class="tittle_agile_w3">Digital Production</h4>
            <div class="heading-underline">
                <div class="h-u1"></div><div class="h-u2"></div><div class="h-u3"></div><div class="clearfix"></div>
            </div>
            <p>From concept to completion, our creative team is with you every step of the way. We will write and develop a script, go on location and film, direct, edit, and deliver a final product you are satisfied with. </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mid_agile_bannner_top_info">
            <h4 class="tittle_agile_w3">Music Videos</h4>
            <div class="heading-underline">
                <div class="h-u1"></div><div class="h-u2"></div><div class="h-u3"></div><div class="clearfix"></div>
            </div>
            <p>A music video integrates song and imagery, produced for promotional or artistic purposes. In Media Gate Studios we use a wide range of styles of contemporary video making techniques, to interpret a professional and creative images and scenes with a thematic and creative approach.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mid_agile_bannner_top_info">
            <h4 class="tittle_agile_w3">Gaming Studios  </h4>
            <div class="heading-underline">
                <div class="h-u1"></div><div class="h-u2"></div><div class="h-u3"></div><div class="clearfix"></div>
            </div>
            <p>The game industry has increased within the media workplace ,Media Gate Studio saw that is a must to have an impact in providing out of the box gaming with studios that are highly qualified with equipments that meet worldwide expectations.</p>
        </div>
        <h3 class="tittle_agile_w3">Images</h3>
        <div class="heading-underline">
            <div class="h-u1"></div><div class="h-u2"></div><div class="h-u3"></div><div class="clearfix"></div>
        </div>
        <ul class="portfolio_agile_info_w3ls">
            @foreach (var item in Directory.GetFiles(Server.MapPath("~/Uploads/Protoflio/Img")))
            {
                string name = Path.GetFileNameWithoutExtension(item);
                <li>
                    <div class="agile_events_top_grid">
                        <div class="w3_agileits_evets_text_img">
                            <a href="~/Uploads/Protoflio/Img/@(name).jpg" class="lsb-preview" data-lsb-group="header">
                                <div class="view view-eighth">
                                    <img src="~/Uploads/Protoflio/Img/@(name).jpg" alt="" class="img-responsive" />
                                    <div class="mask">
                                        <i class="fa fa-eye" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="agileits_w3layouts_events_text port_info_agile">
                            <h3>@Model.Find(x => x.ID == int.Parse(name)).Name</h3>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </li>
            }
        </ul>
    </div>
    <h3 class="tittle_agile_w3">Videos</h3>
    <div class="heading-underline">
        <div class="h-u1"></div><div class="h-u2"></div><div class="h-u3"></div><div class="clearfix"></div>
    </div>
    <ul class="portfolio_agile_info_w3ls test">
        @foreach (string item in Directory.GetFiles(Server.MapPath("~/Uploads/Protoflio/Videos")))
        {
            string name = Path.GetFileNameWithoutExtension(item);
            string S = Model.Find(x => x.ID == int.Parse(name)).Name;
            <li>
                <div class="agile_events_top_grid">
                    <video controls="controls">
                        <source src="~/Uploads/Protoflio/Videos/@(name).mp4" type="video/mp4" />
                    </video>
                    <div class="agileits_w3layouts_events_text port_info_agile">
                        <h3>@S</h3>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
        }
        </ul>
        <br />
        <div>
            <h3 class="tittle_agile_w3">Download Protofolio PDF Files</h3>
            <div class="heading-underline">
                <div class="h-u1"></div><div class="h-u2"></div><div class="h-u3"></div><div class="clearfix"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
       <table class="table">
            <tr>
                <th><h2> File Name</h2></th>
            </tr>
            @foreach (var item in Directory.GetFiles(Server.MapPath("~/Uploads/Protoflio/pdf")))
            {
                int a = int.Parse(Path.GetFileNameWithoutExtension(item));
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <h3> @Model.Find(X => X.ID == a).Name </h3>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        @Html.ActionLink("Download", "Download", new { @id = a }, new { @class = "buttonDownload" })
                    </td>
                </tr>
            }
        </table>
</div>
